128 for ðon, gif ðæt soð is ðæt ðær gecweden is,
129 hi scoldon beon fram forwyrde gehealdene”.

130 Þa englas, broðor, and þæt soðfæste rice
131 on ðam ðu eart, magon beon gecweden gesceapene,
